{"tid":1691650,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[日常文宣] [文宣方向] 以子之矛，攻子之盾","createTime":"2019-11-03T17:54:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T18:30:58.000Z","uid":307203,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"874a7d342132b631f6c826c209c63722f79f2c0c","tid":1691650,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:54:53.000Z","msg":"話說我哋之前用「曱甴」呢個詞語去形容甴近平<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.用推甴近平推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n2.<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">喺Yahoo同Google 同時用習近平同甴近平，而變成聯想詞</span></span><br />\n詳情可以睇返下面：<br />\n<br />\n教你點玩：曱甴王 甴近平<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1684667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1684667</a><br />\n<br />\n[警世] [成績表] 請停止再打&ldquo;甴近平&ldquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1687444\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1687444</a><br />\n<br />\n入黎花一分鐘時間，令習近平名譽掃地<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1685371\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1685371</a><br />\n<br />\n支持&ldquo;甴近平&rdquo;，由你我做起<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1685916\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1685916</a><br />\n<br />\n甚至到近排，蔥友同巴絲一齊玩呢個詞語玩到第二個層次<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.中共領袖名稱</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C6aUcqr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC6aUcqr.png&h=3b04f317&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">2.六四坦克車</span></span><br />\n［品蔥］轉載 曱甴似唔似六四坦克<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1687481\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1687481</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">3.直接喺使用者面前賦予第二種意思</span></span><br />\n一陣如果聽到有狗/藍叫我地「曱甴」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1687761\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1687761</a><br />\n<br />\n我正式宣佈沙田首都走在潮流尖端<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1690910\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1690910</a><br />\n<br />\n重點係我哋可以<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反用對家嘅非人化用詞</span></strong></span>，而<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">創造出新嘅中國牆內禁詞</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />既然我哋香港人可以讓PEPE 有另一種意思，又可以用曱甴去形容習總同警賊<br />\n<br />\n所以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">點解我哋唔將呢種「以子之矛，攻子之盾」嘅方式日常化同普及化呢</span></span>？<br />\n<br />\n雖然係微小嘅行動，但<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">每創造一個敏感詞</span></span>，就能<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">永久搞到中國人失去該詞的使用權</span></span>，搞到佢哋<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無法正常說話</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不如我哋下面討論一下<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">點樣充分騎劫藍絲同三毛嘅用詞</span></span>"},{"pid":"774d86ceb90b78803b4333ade2dfc3829f53b06a","tid":1691650,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:56:05.000Z","msg":"雖然P牌仔推唔到<br />\n但係都要推啊<br />\n<br />\n甴近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f60b37ea2db38e6a72fce5c20b574312f9d1851f","tid":1691650,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:56:21.000Z","msg":"甴近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmo